{"tid":1567964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下咩情況去幫拖先唔叫送頭","createTime":"2019-09-14T07:54:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T10:15:36.000Z","uid":38255,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0b6c1e328fb9b29f9f47c5157a8926cc56aaa661","tid":1567964,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:54:35.000Z","msg":"講到淘大無人住咁，淘大本身係觀塘區算黃，咁淘大當區手足落街趕走班攪自己屋企既畀人圍，去幫拖叫送頭的話，咁要去到咩級數先值得去？<br />\n有街坊就快畀人打死？藍屍捉左個女街坊強姦？一或就算咁嚴重都唔去送頭因為好重防當當區手足係condom？<br />\n一或藍屍踩場果陣就當區居民自行戒嚴留係屋企，由佢地破壞晒自己社區，走左人先落樓，繼續縮長佢地氣焰？"},{"pid":"a08eb7225f13b38578094cf6a9f12ad03d0c11c9","tid":1567964,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:55:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktW8Y1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktW8Y1Q.jpg&h=d39b859f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1veB7Va.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1veB7Va.jpg&h=d08508ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f3a20262dd96c380e41201704be7440adc49e7e","tid":1567964,"uid":59297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:55:47.000Z","msg":"喺啲狗未增援到之前，街坊即落樓一人一拳打死啲藍絲"},{"pid":"17e2371241e7ccd4baaab8fd1de9af65dc3f1680","tid":1567964,"uid":54303,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:58:02.000Z","msg":"我覺得應該學下對家，係條街上面見到藍絲就打（要打到殘廢），有個別出名既就點佢相麻包袋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n白色恐怖係樣好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a85775f23347c11ea879da389757736d3fcadcb0","tid":1567964,"uid":38255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:07:16.000Z","msg":"其實ifc果日係成功例子，夠多人咪騎劫返個場<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今日個個話送頭唔去就真係送頭啦。<br />\n<br />\n雖然今次果班好似暴力好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66e692d453f6